  <title xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">CSR-facility: Fashion Links - Access to Sustainable Production</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The main objective is to create incentives for sustainable production for the Danish fashion industry while achieving a positive effect on the development work in the production countries. 

The project milestones are:
1. Create a greater awareness about sustainability in the Dansh fashion industry, particularly how to implement responsible supply chain management.

2. Develop a database that specifically caters for sustainable production in certain developing countries, thereby making it easier for the Danish fashion industry to identify production partners with a sustainable focus.

3. Facilitate direct contact between Danish fashion brands and potential production partners with a sustainable profile in developing countries by arranging speed-dating events in Copenhagen.</narrative>
  </description>
